65.4	Philip_Kotler	Philip Kotler	Philip Kotler (born 27 May 1931 in Chicago) is an American academic focused on marketing. The author of Marketing Management among dozens of other textbooks and books, he is the S.C. Johnson &amp; Son Distinguished Professor of International Marketing at the Kellogg School of Management at Northwestern University. The nine volume Legends in Marketing: Philip Kotler published in 2012 collects over 150 of his articles, with critical commentary.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/74/Kotler-DSC_0510.jpg/220px-Kotler-DSC_0510.jpg
